{"tid":688464,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭智百戰贏泰國 納比：可擊敗亞洲任何球隊！","createTime":"2018-06-03T08:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T11:22:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b25e29193a618529fe70bd8a8191f2e4175ee522","tid":688464,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/212/21660778212/21662013465_600x387.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F212%2F21660778212%2F21662013465_600x387.jpg&h=55644c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=EKBlxs2ezAfNZLerYJAvGzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=411d63c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】中國在周六友賽作客以2:0輕取泰國，教練納比賽後豪言在亞洲範圍內可戰勝任何對手！<br />\n<br />\n中國今戰有37歲的中場隊長鄭智第100次為國家隊披甲，雨戰下憑武磊在上半場成功執雞、下半場在反擊建功，個人梅開二度，以2:0擊敗有主場之利的泰國。<br />\n<br />\n納比（Marcello Lippi）賽後大讚泰國組織力強，指國足今場擊敗對方，可提升信心：「我們仍然是一支很新的球隊，之前跟歐洲球隊踢了數場都落敗，不過在亞洲範圍內，以我們的能力可以戰勝任何對手。大家非常團結，表現出進攻意欲，而且狀態亦達到我們的要求。」<br />\n<br />\n武磊近2場轟入3球，納比認為這名上海上港鋒將越踢越好：「他之前入球少，所以自己慢慢調整心態，今次入了3球，證明他正在成長。再者，這場是隊長的第100場比賽，球隊亦勝出，我為此感到開心。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"bdd95e4d955e1213d22c869a2140b46518b08822","tid":688464,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:50:17.000Z","msg":"厲害了 我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51732663d6a6cb54c353fcac373b11ac84303e44","tid":688464,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"日韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4765a7e66a99bc69cb9907ef14967584d0f40b6","tid":688464,"uid":4139,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"51732663d6a6cb54c353fcac373b11ac84303e44","tid":688464,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:58: